      <title>特朗普将访问巴黎庆祝巴黎圣母院重新开放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/trump-will-visit-paris-to-celebrate-reopening-of-notre-dame</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普计划于周六前往巴黎参加巴黎圣母院的重新开放仪式，该教堂在 2019 年遭受大火毁坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/trump-will-visit-paris-to-celebrate-reopening-of-notre-dame</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 00:47:03 GMT</pubDate>
