    <item>
      <title>越南最大诈骗案大亨寻求避免被处决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/mogul-seeks-to-avoid-execution-in-vietnam-s-biggest-fraud-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南房地产大亨张美兰（Truong My Lan）即将接受听证，以确定她是否会被免于死刑。法庭正准备就她对死刑判决的上诉作出裁决，她因策划了该国有史以来最大的欺诈丑闻而被判处死刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/mogul-seeks-to-avoid-execution-in-vietnam-s-biggest-fraud-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国政府濒临崩溃，面临“关键时刻”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/france-faces-moment-of-truth-as-government-poised-to-collapse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 警告议员们，法国已经到了“关键时刻”，极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 将加入左翼联盟，最早于本周推翻其政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/france-faces-moment-of-truth-as-government-poised-to-collapse</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登赦免儿子为何如此有争议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/why-joe-biden-pardoning-his-son-hunter-is-so-controversial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[围绕亨特·拜登正在进行的法律纠纷戛然而止，因为他的父亲、美国总统乔·拜登赦免了亨特·拜登的税务和枪支指控（尽管他曾发誓不会这么做）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/why-joe-biden-pardoning-his-son-hunter-is-so-controversial</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 22:59:06 GMT</pubDate>
