      <title>特朗普任命投资银行家沃伦·斯蒂芬斯为英国大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/trump-picks-investment-banker-warren-stephens-as-uk-ambassador</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提名投资银行家沃伦·斯蒂芬斯担任美国驻英国大使，任命一位著名的共和党捐助者和商人担任他第二届政府的主要外交职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/trump-picks-investment-banker-warren-stephens-as-uk-ambassador</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 22:05:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
