      <title>分析人士称特朗普胜选后墨西哥商业环境将恶化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/trump-s-win-sees-pessimism-on-business-climate-deepen-in-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥分析人士预测，唐纳德·特朗普在美国总统大选中获胜后，未来六个月的商业环境将出现负面转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/trump-s-win-sees-pessimism-on-business-climate-deepen-in-mexico</guid>
